description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
- Clownfish and sea anemone
- Blue Sea of Kerama, Okinawa
- School of bigeye trevally
- Colorful fishes in the tropical sea
- Coral reefs and skin diver
- Sea turtle
- Group of Chromis viridis
- Jellyfish
- School of Tuna
- Luna lionfish
name: Underwater Photography
